title: Deitel & Deitel How to Program Collection
description:
This torrent includes the following books:

C How to Program (7th edition,latest accordsing to Deitel's site)
C++ How to program (8th edition,most recent edition is 9th)
Java How to program (10th edition,most recent edition according to Deitel's site)
Android How to program (1st edition,most recent edition is 2nd)
C# 2012 How to program (5th edition,most recent edition according to Deitel's site)

This torrent does NOT include the source code examples,but these and other materials can be downloaded for free on the official website http://www.deitel.com/Default.aspx

Just click on the book and the link to the source code examples will be there (registration may be required,but it's free too).

I couldn't find the most recent editions of the android and C++ books,if you have them or know where they are please share on the comments.

Education must be free.

Enjoy the torrent!
